# {{project_name}}

Multi-algorithm RL with PyTorch Lightning + Hydra + Gymnasium. Ships with SAC, TD3, PPO (discrete + continuous), RPO, and DQN.

## Commands

{% if deps_manager == 'pixi' -%}
```bash
pixi run train       # launch training (algorithm set in config)
pixi run test        # run test suite
pixi run lint        # ruff check
```
{%- elif deps_manager == 'uv' -%}
```bash
uv run invoke train  # launch training
uv run invoke test   # run test suite
uv run ruff check .  # lint
```
{%- else -%}
```bash
invoke train         # launch training
invoke test          # run test suite
ruff check .         # lint
```
{%- endif %}

Switch algorithm and environment entirely via config — no code changes:
```bash
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py +experiment=sac_pendulum
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py +experiment=ppo_cartpole
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py +experiment=dqn_lunar_lander
```

## Architecture

**Algorithm selection is config-only.** `configs/train_config.yaml` `defaults` list selects the agent config (e.g., `agent: sac`). Each agent config points to its LightningModule via `_target_`.

**Each algorithm module is self-contained** — no shared base class:
- `sac_module.py` / `td3_module.py` — off-policy actor-critic
- `ppo_module.py` — on-policy (also handles RPO)
- `dqn_module.py` — off-policy value-based

**Data pipeline splits by on/off-policy:**
- `data/replay_buffer.py` + `data/env_datamodule.py` — SAC, TD3, DQN
- `data/rollout_datamodule.py` — PPO, RPO

**Callbacks are optional but wired in configs:**
- `callbacks/episode_logger.py` — logs episode reward and length to WandB
- `callbacks/video_logger.py` — records env renders (disable by removing from config; slow)

**Models are pure networks** — `models/actor.py` and `models/critic.py` return raw tensors. All RL logic (Bellman update, entropy tuning, GAE) lives in the module files.

## Key files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `src/{{repo_name}}/<algo>_module.py` | Algorithm logic — extend the relevant one |
| `src/{{repo_name}}/data/replay_buffer.py` | Off-policy experience replay |
| `src/{{repo_name}}/data/rollout_datamodule.py` | On-policy trajectory collection |
| `configs/experiment/` | Preset configs per algorithm + environment |
| `configs/agent/` | Per-algorithm hyperparameters |
| `configs/environment/` | Gymnasium env configs |
